responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "F4F88FFA4A5768AD8C928495D694B039", "My ancestors, they feel your urgency, yes. But I cannot join you. Moot, it is fragile. I must stay, help smooth things over with Elders. They need reassurance, and I cannot afford to be absent.")
